{"tid":1300821,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日放榜嘅中學雞全部同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-09T13:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T04:08:46.000Z","uid":78907,"like":197,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"66577e0bf3597da898220124d6b276838412bd04","tid":1300821,"uid":78907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"聽日放榜我知大家都好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n達唔到目標的確係一件灰心嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且香港呢一排嘅氣氛的確都好灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但大家聽日無論點都好 都千其<br />\n唔好諗住<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死</span></span></strong><br />\n唔好諗住做<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">義士</span></span></strong><br />\n因為呢個世界冇話您短暫失敗就冇人生義意嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要相信自己會同香港一樣 ！所有嘢都會好轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmk d講句 聽日一定會好天嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚我會係到同大家傾計 大家想傾乜都得 <br />\n各位巴絲唔嫌棄嘅就入嚟吹兩嘴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fd33947e6cb8dd8272747ddbe6d30f3c63f73e","tid":1300821,"uid":78907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83140cb8b534b6a95e1ff771dc6d76812d3edd89","tid":1300821,"uid":105888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8272734b56446952f432cf1ed5a030a3a5e7ed2","tid":1300821,"uid":82359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"無錯 記住一持挫敗唔等於一世<br />\n你未來仲會有好多機會"},{"pid":"4023ff3afb145722639a525429